Client.CM_Instruct: WATCH FOR SPECIAL INSTRUCTIONS.  MAY SHOW "PRIVATE LABEL." IF SO, DO NOT IDENTIFY YOURSELF AS BEING THERE ON BEHALF OF GE.  USE COMPANY LISTED NEXT TO "PRIVATE LABEL."  UNLESS SPECIFICALLY NOTED, DO NOT SAY YOU ARE THERE ON BEHALF OF GE. UNDER NO CIRCUMSTANCES ARE YOU TO PICK UP A CHECK OR VISIT A RESIDENCE. THE PURPOSE OF THE INSPECTION IS TO GET THE CONTACT ON THE PHONE WITH GE.  CHECK SPECIAL INSTRUCTIONS FOR DIRECTION ON PHONE CLEARANCE. DO NOT LEAVE CALL-BACK CARD, LEAVE THE LETTER INCLUDED WITH THE REMINDER FORM.  CONTACT QT IF IT IS NOT ATTACHED TO JOB OR EMAILED.  PHONE CLEARANCE IN PERSON IS REQUIRED ON ALL GE INSPECTIONS AND GE CLOSES AT 4PM CT.  CRITICAL THAT YOU GET THE LESSEE ON THE PHONE WITH GE.  IF UNABLE TO GET THROUGH, LEAVE A MESSAGE WITH THE JOB NAME AND REFERENCE NUMBER AND YOUR CONTACT INFORMATION.  DO NOT LEAVE UNTIL YOU HAVE SPOKEN TO GE.  IF NO LUCK AFTER 20 MIN., CONTACT QUIKTRAK.

Inspector.IM_RemNote: 2/22/2018 JMV-- Jim has asked to be inactivated, effective 3/2/18.
